title: Metaform--Brick and Mortar
description:
Oh hell yeah folks!!!

Its ya man Jojo once again bringing you that hot mp3 wax taken right off the mixing board.  Hey, an intern has to get paid somehow right?

This is the one, the hot slammer that won Metaform the URB 1000.

"BRICK AND MORTAR"
From the upcoming album "Standing on the Shoulders of Giants", April 15, 2008.

This kid is on the rise in a major way.

Check out this track, it is the hottest thing out in 08.

Enjoy.
